{"tid":1092530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7旬漢與妻爭執 向4歲兒箍頸洩憤被捕","createTime":"2019-04-05T02:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T05:45:06.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0328fde850b6766839f6ed6edd5f0c72aa2292df","tid":1092530,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Noo4oVV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNoo4oVV.png&h=fb1a477b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌石籬邨石歡樓一單位，早上7時，姓葉（70歲）男子與40歲姓楊妻子，因事發生爭執，其間葉情緒激動，竟向年僅4歲兒子箍頸洩憤。葉妻見狀報警求助，經警員調查，兒子頸痛無表面傷痕，葉則手及嘴部受傷，涉虐兒被捕後，由警員押解下送院治理。"},{"pid":"a861cf9557af10bb6d0261c7cb88dcdaf84335e9","tid":1092530,"uid":218082,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:21:35.000Z","msg":"70歲嘅廢老有個40歲嘅老婆,4歲嘅仔<br />\n真係IP都唔洗check都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38983795bfe0f480dea4a30060ebf4667520e7a","tid":1092530,"uid":37747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:22:37.000Z","msg":"60幾歲先學人生仔仲打仔，正仆街"},{"pid":"c777f0edfe22633a0136e5e27254eeffcd31021d","tid":1092530,"uid":24909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"跟住同佢離婚 踢佢出間公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢老上報紙扮可憐 劇本黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16981771d0caa6d870677f927791207824024b0","tid":1092530,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:26:38.000Z","msg":"又多一個廢老成功比支那婆踢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5634f1c67409413cbc32b4affb8eecc26285ce5f","tid":1092530,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c777f0edfe22633a0136e5e27254eeffcd31021d","tid":1092530,"uid":24909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"跟住同佢離婚 踢佢出間公屋<img src=\"/as